name: Capture the planet: Cute War
description:
Have you ever tried to shoot a slingshot? And tried to shoot from a slingshot of fluffy animals? If not, then this game is made especially for you. In the game you have to shoot a slingshot funny animals, in order to destroy the buildings that prevent them from living normally.In this arcade you will find a lot of exciting levels that will not leave indifferent even
the most demanding fan of the game.


Feature of game

- A large number of levels
- Beautiful graphics
- Lovely animals
- Suitable for children and adults
- Great background music
